    "en": {
      "title": "One person died in Ambalangoda firing range",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambalangoda police say that one person was killed and two others were seriously injured in a shooting that took place in a hotel in Delduwa area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda.",
        "The police say that Dhanushka De Soysa (32), a resident of Madampe Maharuppa area of \u200b\u200bAmbalangoda, died in this shooting.",
        "This is the third shooting that took place in Ambalangoda within a month and the police say that three people were killed and two were injured in the previous two shootings."
      ],
